{"tid":2417837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比特幣漲勢面臨市場流動性下降的潛在考驗","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T07:35:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a57c5db69dc8ddef2c8d5b52455c2f7a40e059ad","tid":2417837,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XXEnikogXYfxzrLCsns0PA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/FWx9PUEOJI7sapkobVCTbQ--~B/aD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/42dfd8aef9f0dcdc5fff7a5611834647\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXXEnikogXYfxzrLCsns0PA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFWx9PUEOJI7sapkobVCTbQ--~B%2FaD02NzU7dz0xMjAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fbloomberg_chinese_traditional_757%2F42dfd8aef9f0dcdc5fff7a5611834647&h=e459d258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 比特幣漲勢推動價格在周末觸及新峰值，但可能面對流動性下降的考驗。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣周日一度漲至58,350美元，在東京時間周一下午2:30跌至約56,200美元。據摩根大通的策略師Nikolaos Panigirtzoglou，比特幣過去三個月已上漲約兩倍，但比特幣市場的流動性已惡化。<br />\n<br />\n他上周五在一份報告中寫道，「目前，比特幣市場的流動性遠低於黃金或標普500指數，這意味著即使很小的資金流動也會對價格產生重大影響。」<br />\n<br />\n這種背景為比特幣的上漲和下跌都開啟了可能性，取決於對數字資產的普遍熱情。最近，就連比特幣的一些最大支持者似乎都對其崛起之勢感到驚訝。伊隆&middot;馬斯克在近期的推文中稱，比特幣價格「似乎很高」。<br />\n<br />\nPanigirtzoglou寫道，比特幣現貨和期貨市場的總交易額每天約為100億美元，而黃金的當量數據在1000億美元，這與「比特幣流動性比黃金低得多」的說法一致。"},{"pid":"f04baef87f6f891b9a4109e2c85d6671572397e5","tid":2417837,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:35:46.000Z","msg":"係啊 快D沽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}